&lt;p&gt;三月七日，沙湖道中遇雨。雨具先去，同行皆狼狈，余独不觉，已而遂晴，故作此词。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;</description></item><item><title>读《今日简史》</title><link>https://xuchengpeng.cn/posts/reading-21-lessons-for-the-21st-century/</link><pubDate>Mon, 04 Aug 2025 16:17:34 +0800</pubDate><author>chuckxcp@qq.com (Chuck)</author><guid>https://xuchengpeng.cn/posts/reading-21-lessons-for-the-21st-century/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;人类命运大议题。&lt;/p&gt;
